{"id": 2994, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，哪些社交媒体上的万能“缓冲带”你已经离不开了？", "description": "一些介于“在线分享”和“在线自闭”之间的“半公开”地带。（题图来自：iStock ©️ VictoriaBar）", "record_count": 6786, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190908214059oIEFGp12BHJyAN37.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-09T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5901, "title": "现如今，哪些社交媒体上的万能“缓冲带”你已经离不开了？", "content": "你在社交媒体上都发现了哪些万能的“缓冲带”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 346195, "content": "“三天可见/分组展示”，既能表达又不会暴露太多", "image": "img/option/option/20190908212131gTSxZwMhO8kLcn0Q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346196, "content": "“哈哈哈”/表情包/猫片，线上聊天缓和气氛必备", "image": "img/option/option/20190908220611xNlcq3stMZdTm2zD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346197, "content": "社交平台小号，避开熟人默默吐槽专用", "image": "img/option/option/20190908213032nkUQsLWt1eVjldmx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346198, "content": "微博“仅半年内可见”，避开很多无意义的争执", "image": "img/option/option/201909082120591lQZ0tnWiMXdgcTF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346199, "content": "用饭否/即刻等相对小众的平台，有趣又不会太多人", "image": "img/option/option/201909082119572QAJkCUSfYi3We4l.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346200, "content": "“屏蔽/拉黑/不看xx好友”等功能，眼不见心不烦", "image": "img/option/option/20190908211832XrYUDuxZ4K1nTfEz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346201, "content": "豆瓣/网易云音乐等评论区，跟网友唠嗑还不用真的交朋友", "image": "img/option/option/20190908204701Z0XGHObfno5vNa87.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346203, "content": "对我来说，所有社交媒体都是线下人际关系的缓冲", "image": "img/option/option/20190908220423XIl4uH2kxdjYEv6R.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}